devdoc.title: This contract converts a kitty's genes into binary, kai notation, and cattributes and stores them in mappings

binaryToKai(uint256).notice: converts binary to its corresponding kai notationonly dominant genes are kept since kitties only demonstrate cattributes from dominant genes.

fillKaiValue().notice: mapping a gene in binary with its kai notation

getDominantGeneBinary(uint256,uint256).notice: converts the gene in uint of a kitty to binary.only dominant genes are kept since kitties only demonstrate cattributes from dominant genes.

kaiToCattribute(uint256).notice: converts kai notation to its corresponding cattribute

toBinaryString(uint256).notice: converts an integer to its binary
